item.title: Walker Ranch Hike 5/22/2020
item.description: Some photos of hiking the Walker Ranch Loop starting from the Boulder trail head View down the valley near the start Bird that let met take its photo Bench overlooking the valley Smaller bird that let me take its photo Shot of the trail near the start Bunny eating grass along the trail in the heavy wooded section Some rocks on the trail Little zen waterfall Bridge over the rapids flowing creek Creek rapids from snow melt Rock portion next to rapids waterfall (small) Start of stair ascent View from the high valley along the trail Just an amazing view Some information on the creek and Gentle Power
